        "words": [
          {
            "word": "What",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "什么"
          },
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_4",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "Why does the idea of progress loom so large in the modern world?",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 15.87,
      "endTime": 21.4,
      "analysis": {
        "grammar": [
          {
            "text": "does",
            "label": "助动词"
          }
        ],
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s1",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Surely because progress of a particular kind is actually taking place around us",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 21.41,
      "endTime": 27.62,
      "analysis": {
        "grammar": [
          {
            "text": "is",
            "label": "谓语/系动词"
          }
        ],
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s2",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "and is becoming more and more manifest.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 27.63,
      "endTime": 30.3,
      "analysis": {
        "grammar": [
          {
            "text": "is",
            "label": "谓语/系动词"
          }
        ],
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s3",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Although mankind has undergone no general improvement in intelligence or morality,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 30.31,
      "endTime": 36.15
    },
    {
      "id": "s4",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "it has made extraordinary progress in the accumulation of knowledge.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 36.16,
      "endTime": 41.36,
      "analysis": {
        "grammar": [
          {
            "text": "it",
            "label": "人称代词/主语"
          }
        ],
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s5",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Knowledge began to increase as soon as the thoughts of one individual",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 41.37,
      "endTime": 45.68
    },
    {
      "id": "s6",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "could be communicated to another by means of speech.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 45.69,
      "endTime": 50.01
    },
    {
      "id": "s7",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "With the invention of writing, a great advance was made,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 50.02,
      "endTime": 53.66
    },
    {
      "id": "s8",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "for knowledge could then be not only communicated but also stored.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 53.67,
      "endTime": 58.65,
      "analysis": {
        "grammar": [],
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s9",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Libraries made education possible, and education in its turn added to libraries:",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 58.66,
      "endTime": 65.38,
      "analysis": {
        "grammar": [
          {
            "text": "its",
            "label": "形容词性物主代词"
          }
        ],
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s10",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "the growth of knowledge followed a kind of compound interest law,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 65.39,
      "endTime": 70.22
    },
    {
      "id": "s11",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "which was greatly enhanced by the invention of printing.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 70.23,
      "endTime": 74.02
    },
    {
      "id": "s12",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "All this was comparatively slow until, with the coming of science,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 74.03,
      "endTime": 79.52,
      "analysis": {
        "grammar": [
          {
            "text": "this",
            "label": "指示代词"
          }
        ],
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s13",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "the tempo was suddenly raised.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 79.53,
      "endTime": 81.94
    },
    {
      "id": "s14",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Then knowledge began to be accumulated according to a systematic plan.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 81.95,
      "endTime": 87.43
    },
    {
      "id": "s15",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The trickle became a stream: the stream has now become a torrent.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 87.44,
      "endTime": 92.97
    },
    {
      "id": "s16",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Moreover, as soon as new knowledge is acquired, it is now turned to practical account.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 92.98,
      "endTime": 99.17,
      "analysis": {
        "grammar": [
          {
            "text": "is",
            "label": "谓语/系动词"
